WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  Remember when you were younger and used to chew bubble gum?
'BulGom' is a reminder of those bygone days when the bubbles
formed with the gum used to blow up in the face... Now is the time
to take your revenge!

  'BulGom' is a Workbench game in which you have to burst bubbles,
the amount of points you get is calculated according to the number
of burst bubbles. You get much more points if those bubbles are
all of the same colour...

  However, there is a little complication: bubbles of 4 different
sizes appear on the game board. To burst a bubble it must be at
its maximum size; you have to click on the smaller bubbles to
increase their size before you can burst them. Additionally, when
a bubble is clicked on and it does not burst at least one other
bubble, a new bubble will appear on the game board.

  Do not let the board fill up completely because if it happens,
the game will be over.

  Have fun!

